rows.label: qev090202_MSG0001
rows.name: Huh. Wreckage from the White Whale in Oblivia, eh?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090202_MSG0002
rows.name: I don't think any Reclaimers have been out that way yet.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090202_MSG0003
rows.name:
Could be the mother lode.
Put every discovery up until now to shame![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090202_MSG0004
rows.name: I'm sold, pard. Sold HARD![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090202_JNK0010
rows.name: Urge

rows.label: qev090202_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Yelv what he is waiting for.

rows.label: qev090202_JNK0020
rows.name: Resist

rows.label: qev090202_SEL0021
rows.name: Wonder aloud if there are more pressing missions.

rows.label: qev090202_MSG0005
rows.name: Nothin' and nobody![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090202_MSG0006
rows.name: Anythin' I want to do is pressin' as far as you're concerned![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090202_MSG0007
rows.name: Quicker you learn that little number, the better.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090202_MSG0008
rows.name: Next stop, Oblivia. Let's go find us some ship guts![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090202_MSG0009
rows.name:
Huh. Some freak swarm of native critters
that needs exterminatin'...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090202_MSG0010
rows.name:
Man, I hate those things.
Always fulla tentacles and eyes and crap. Ugh.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090202_MSG0011
rows.name: Eh, what do you think? Do it anyway?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090202_JNK0030
rows.name: Confirm

rows.label: qev090202_SEL0031
rows.name: Tell Yelv that it is important BLADE work.

rows.label: qev090202_JNK0040
rows.name: Reject

rows.label: qev090202_SEL0041
rows.name: Say that it sounds boring.

rows.label: qev090202_MSG0012_m
rows.name: Pffft. Look at the goody two-shoes. Lighten up, will ya?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090202_MSG0012_f
rows.name: Pffft. Look at the goody two-shoes. Lighten up, will ya?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090202_MSG0013
rows.name: Meh, let's go.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090202_MSG0014
rows.name: Damn right![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090202_MSG0015
rows.name:
Though I SUPPOSE a gig like that
is a way to earn some quick cash...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090202_MSG0016
rows.name: Meh, let's just bang it out for giggles.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090202_MSG0017
rows.name: Oh, and don't forget...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090202_MSG0018
rows.name: Once we're done with this, we gotta report back to Eleonora.[ST:wait ]
